{
  "title": "linux中使用第三方yum源解决办法",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Yum</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">永久解决方案</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">首先要确保网络是畅通的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ping</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">命令测试</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">进入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/etc/yum.repos.d/</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目录</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在命令行输入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">wget&nbsp;<a href=\"http://docs.linuxtone.org/soft/lemp/CentOS-Base.repo%E5%9C%A8%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%8B%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0CentOS-\">http://docs.linuxtone.org/soft/lemp/CentOS-Base.repo</a></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><a href=\"http://docs.linuxtone.org/soft/lemp/CentOS-Base.repo%E5%9C%A8%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%8B%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0CentOS-\">在当前目录下得到</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://docs.linuxtone.org/soft/lemp/CentOS-Base.repo%E5%9C%A8%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%8B%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0CentOS-\">CentOS-</a>&nbsp;Base.repo</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">mv CentOS-Base.repo rhel-debuginfo.repo</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">命令修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CentOS- Base.repo</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">文件名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">yum check-update</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">测试是否成功</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这个方案是临时性的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">安装第三方的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">yum</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">源</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">安装</span>yum-priorities<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">插件</span>&nbsp;yum install yum-priorities</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">下载第三方的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">yum</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">源（以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">epel</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">为例）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">下载地址是：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/5/i386/repoview/epel-release.html\">http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/5/i386/repoview/epel-release.html</a></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">rpm –vih</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">安装就可以了，安装完成以后修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/etc/yum.repos.d/epel.repo</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">文件，添加</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">priority=11</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，安装</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">repoforge&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">源</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">下载地址是：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://pkgs.repoforge.org/rpmforge-release/\">http://pkgs.repoforge.org/rpmforge-release/</a></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">安装完成以后修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/etc/yum.repos.d/rpmforge.repo</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">文件，添加</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">priority=12</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，检查安装是否成功可以重启系统以后输入：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">yum check-update</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">或者使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">yum install</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">命令安装一个软件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><br><br><br><br><h1><span class=\"ask-title \">在centos中yum-priorities这个是什么文件?</span></h1><br><pre id=\"best-content-1614104422\" class=\"best-text mb-10\">yum源优先级的一个文件。<br>是yum-plugin-priroites这个插件的一个文件。<br>用来给yum源分优先级的。<br>比如你在centos下有centos，epel，rpmfusion三个yum源。<br>三个yum源中可能含有相同的软件，补丁之类的东西。<br>yum管理器为了分辨更新系统或者安装软件的时候用那个yum源的软件所以才有这么个东西。<br>如果说，设置centos官方的yum源优先级最高，epelyum源第二，rpmfusion第三。（用1到99来表示，1最高）<br>那在安装程序的时候，先寻找centos的yum源，如果源里面有要的程序，那就停止寻找，直接安装找到的，如果没有找到，就依次寻找epel和rpmfusion的源。<br>如果说三个yum源都含有同一个软件，那就安装优先级最高的yum源的。<br>就是这么个东西~~~</pre></div>"
    }
  ]
}